window.bookSummaryJSON = "A British whaler has been captured by an ambitious chief in the Friendly Isles, and Captain Jack Aubrey is dispatched to restore order. But Jack must first contend with an escaped convict who has stowed away on the <i>Surprise</i>, an attractive female convict who is driving the crew to awkward courtliness and dangerous jealousies. <p>The fifteenth installment of Patrick O'Brian's hugely successful Aubrey/Maturin series.</p>"; 
